{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a certain-- although ghetto was feared, but as well there was a feeling that being--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--among other Jews was somehow safer and better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that of course was felt later as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed until autumn, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the autumn, 1940, the ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although it was formed, it was formed in such a way that the borders of the ghetto were announced in the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- of course, there were newspapers in Warsaw, both German-speaking and Polish-speaking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at this time, there must have been as well Yiddish newspapers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The borders were determined.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when it came to creating the-- forming the ghetto, months later, maybe, closing-- in other words, putting the first the barbed wire fencing and then the walls, it happened that it was really smaller than was originally announced.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So immediately some areas, which were originally going to be inside, were taken out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were unlucky because I think-- well, we had to move because our apartment was outside the ghetto by quite a good distance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father found some apartment to rent in Tlomackie near this big synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then we found out that Tlomackie, after all, was not part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to look for something else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we finally found an apartment in Chlodna Street, Chlodna, I think, 49.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was on the border of ghetto and the Aryan area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, Chlodna was a street which was crossing the dividing between so-called big ghetto and small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- when the-- although the pavements were in the ghetto, the road itself was not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was part of the Aryan quarter.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
